Indianapolis Colts coach Jim Caldwell to work with quarterback
 Joe Flacco , the National Football League team said.  Caldwell, 57, was fired by the Colts after the team
finished the season with a record of 2-14.  Flacco led the Ravens to the American Football Conference
championship game, losing to the New England Patriots 23-20 on
